review_title: If you are over 5'10" It's a tight fit.
reviews:
The suit just barely fits me. I am 5'9" and I had to really duck into the suit in order to get it up and over my head. I also had to wear the feet of the dinosaur a bit up onto my calf in order to see through the screen. A friend who is about 5'5" tried it on and they had a much easier time getting it on and it fit them as I imagine it should.
Instructions were a bit lacking, but not too difficult to install the fans once you realize there is a piece that unscrews on the actual fan.
